<h2>What You Need Before You Build an MCP Server for Marketing</h2>
<p><strong>Time required:</strong> 2 to 4 hours for a basic server. 1 to 2 days for production-ready deployment.</p>
<p><strong>Difficulty:</strong> Intermediate. You need basic TypeScript or JavaScript knowledge.</p>
<p><strong>What you will need:</strong></p>
<ul>
<li>[ ] Node.js 18+ installed on your machine</li>
<li>[ ] A code editor (VS Code or Cursor recommended)</li>
<li>[ ] TypeScript basics (variables, functions, async/await)</li>
