<h2>Step 7: Test, Harden, and Deploy</h2>
<p>Testing an MCP server requires 3 layers: unit tests for individual tools, integration tests for data accuracy, and security hardening for production.</p>
<p><strong>Unit testing each tool:</strong></p>
<p>Call each tool handler with known inputs and verify the output format:</p>
<pre><code class="language-typescript">// Test Google Ads tool
const result = await getGoogleAdsSpend(&#123;
  campaignId: &quot;123456789&quot;,
